    <p style="text-align:left; padding-left: 10px; padding-right:10px; font-size:1.3em;">We treat all ages and most medical issues. We accept most insurance plans and can file claims for you. We offer standard lab tests, x-rays and some additional testing in our office for your convenience. We work with you to decide the best, least intrusive treatments for your particular health care needs. </p>
         
